								h2.g-font-size-32--xs.g-font-size-45--sm.g-font-size-55--md.g-color--white
									| Medical Excellence
									br
									| Every Day
								p.g-font-size-18--xs.g-font-size-22--sm.g-color--white-opacity Clinics can be privately operated or publicly managed and funded.
							a.text-uppercase.s-btn.s-btn--md.s-btn--white-brd.g-radius--50.g-padding-x-50--xs(href='http://themeforest.net/item/metronic-responsive-admin-dashboard-template/4021469?ref=keenthemes') Read More
